[[Jordan national football team|Jordan]] announced a 30-man preliminary squad on May 17.<ref>[https://www.jfa.jo/news.php?id=31152&title=%D8%A5%D8%B9%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%89-%D8%AA%D8%A3%D9%87%D8%A8%D8%A7-%D9%84%D9%85%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%AA%D9%8A-%D8%B3%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D9%88%D9%83%D9%88%D9%84%D9%88%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A7 "إعلان القائمة الأولية لمنتخب النشامى تأهبا لمواجهتي سويسرا وكولومبيا وديا"] [Announcement of the preliminary roster for the Nashama national team ahead of the friendly matches against Switzerland and Colombia] (in Arabic). [[Jordan Football Association]]. May 17, 2026. Retrieved May 18, 2026.</ref> The squad was reduced to 28 players on May 27.<ref>[https://www.jfa.jo/news.php?id=31171&title=%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%89-%D9%8A%D8%AE%D8%AA%D8%AA%D9%85-%D8%AA%D8%AD%D8%B6%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%86..-%D9%88%D9%8A%D8%BA%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA-%D8%BA%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86-%D8%BA%D8%AF%D8%A7 "منتخب النشامى يختتم تحضيراته في عمان.. ويغادر إلى سانت غالن غدا"] (in Arabic). [[Jordan Football Association]]. May 27, 2026. Retrieved May 27, 2026.</ref> Their final squad was announced on June 2.<ref>[https://royanews.com/en/إعلان-قائمة-النشامى-لنهائيات-كأس-العا/ "The Jordanian national team's squad for the 2026 World Cup finals has been announced – Video"]. royanews.com. June 2, 2026.</ref> [[Ibrahim Sabra]] withdrew injured on June 5<ref>[https://x.com/JordanFA/status/2062955822317977881 "أمنيات السلامة والشفاء العاجل للاعب إبراهيم صبرة، والعودة إلى الملاعب في أقرب وقت بعد أن أظهرت الفحوصات الطبية إصابته بتمزق في أربطة الكاحل للقدم اليسرى أثناء التدريبات، ما يستدعي خضوعه لبرنامج علاجي وتأهيلي خلال الفترة المقبلة، واستبعاده من قائمة النشامى لكأس العالم 2026"] [Wishing safety and a speedy recovery for player Ibrahim Sabra, and a return to the fields at the earliest opportunity, after medical examinations revealed his injury with a tear in the ligaments of his left ankle during training, which necessitates his undergoing a treatment and rehabilitation program in the coming period, and his exclusion from the Nashama squad for the 2026 World Cup.] (in Arabic). [[Jordan Football Association]]. June 5, 2026. Retrieved June 5, 2026.</ref> and was replaced by [[Mohammad Taha (footballer)|Mohammad Taha]] on June 8.<ref>[https://x.com/JordanFA/status/2064030556929593647 "قرر الجهاز الفني للنشامى بقيادة المدرب جمال سلامي ضم اللاعب محمد أبو غوش إلى قائمة النشامى لكأس العالم 2026"] [The national team’s technical staff, led by head coach Jamal Sellami, has decided to include the player Mohammad Abu Ghoush in the Nashama squad for the 2026 World Cup] (in Arabic). [[Jordan Football Association]]. June 8, 2026. Retrieved June 5, 2026.</ref>

